{
  "chapter": 34,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"惊人的消息\"，主要场景为孙小红在酒馆与李寻欢对饮交谈。孙小红透露上官金虹之所以动心，是因为听说沈浪曾托李寻欢之父保管两本武功秘笈，而林仙儿散布了这一谣言。李寻欢追问阿飞下落，孙小红取出一幅标注阿飞住处的纸卷交给他。孙小红试图灌醉李寻欢，李寻欢最终醉倒。孙驼子现出真面目，与孙小红对话，揭示孙驼子实为孙白发的二子，伪装身份暗中保护李寻欢。孙小红告知爷爷已出城送走上官金虹，并列举了多位即将找上门的危险人物：大欢喜女菩萨、蓝蝎子、吕凤先、荆无命、胡不归等人，说明李寻欢处境之险。孙小红决定按爷爷安排将醉倒的李寻欢转移避祸。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你看你，老毛病又犯了，还未轮到你问的时候，你偏偏要问。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹这人的脾气，你当然知道，普通的宝藏，自然不能令他动心，这次他怎么会动了心呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为他听说昔年天下第一位名侠沈浪是令尊的好朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "沈大侠的确是先父的道义之交，但他多年前便已买棹东渡，退隐于海外之仙山，却和这件事有何关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我就让你先问一问吧，不然我看你真要憋死了，但你却得先喝三大杯，我才回答你这个问题。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为他听说沈大侠归隐之前，曾托令尊保管两本书，这两本书就是他毕生所练的武功心法，你只练了其中的一本，小李飞刀就已无敌于天下，若是两本都练成，那还得了？所以连上官金虹那样的人也无法不动心了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "若真有这回事，怎会连我自己都不知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我也知道这全是林仙儿造出来的谣言，沈大侠绝世惊才，最了解人心之弱点，又怎会留下什么武功秘笈来让后人争夺？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就算他有武功秘笈要留下，也不会留在你家，他和令尊既然是道义之交，又怎会在你家留下个祸胎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道你心里一定有很多问题想问我，我若不让你赢一次，你不急死才怪，所以我现在要问你的，你一定能回答得出。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你现在心里头是不是还只有她一个人？甚至不惜为她而死……我说的'她'是谁，你自然知道的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "只道无情却有情，情到浓时情转薄……是无情？是有情？又有谁分得清？又有谁……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "多情自古空余恨，你这又是何苦？……又是何苦……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这次我认输了，你问吧，你可以继续问下去，但我若能回答，还是算你输，你还是要喝一杯。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "阿飞现在究竟在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我早就知道你第一句要问的就是这句话了，除了'她'之外，阿飞恐怕就是你最关心的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "无论谁交到他那种朋友，都无法不关心他的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "若有人能交到你这种朋友，岂非也一样无法不关心你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这就是阿飞住的地方，你按图寻访，就能找到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我对你说出了你最切身的秘密，你不谢我，我告诉你是谁要杀你，你也不谢我，现在你为何要谢我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你纵然不说，我也知道，因为你有了这张图，就可以找到阿飞，你只有找到他，才可能救他，劝他莫要对一个不值得爱的女人太迷恋，劝他莫要毁了自己，你是为了他才谢我的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这正如你为了林诗音而谢郭嵩阳一样……你难道永远也不会为了自己说个'谢'字么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我爷爷常说，一个人若是总不为自己着想，活着也未免太可怜了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "一个人若总是为自己着想，活着岂非更可怜？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "孙老爷子出城去接人，却不知接的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "其实他并不是去接人，而是去送人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "送人？送谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上官金虹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "上官金虹根本还未入城，怎会就要走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我爷爷既然是专程去送他的，他怎么好意思不走？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "莫非孙老爷子……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你今天喝得太多，也太快，有什么话，还是留到明天再问吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你可知道上官金虹这个人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我不知道，我也不喝酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你又没有跟我们拼酒，这杯酒你自然用不着喝的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "但我却可以告诉你，上官金虹自命是天下第一高手，一向眼高于顶，目空一切，从来也不肯买任何人的账，这次却买了孙老先生的账，那么你猜，这孙老先生会是什么样的人呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我猜不出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我也猜不出，所以我一定要问，非问明白不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你问得太多，所以你一定醉了，非醉不可。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "醉了又有什么不好？人生难得几回醉！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "孙姑娘，我问你，孙老爷子究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "孙老爷子就是我父亲的父亲，我自己的爷爷。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "不错不错，这回答简直正确极了……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我还有句话要问你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "趁你还未醉的时候，赶快问吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我问你，你为何一心想要灌醉我？为什么……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我本就是要跟你拼酒的，自然要将你灌倒，每个喝酒的人都希望别人比自己先醉倒，你说对不对？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "对，对，对，对极了……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃晚饭的时候到了，只怕又有客人要上门……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "别人都说二叔你是天生神力，偏偏只有我到今天才见到……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "谁是你的二叔？姑娘你莫非也醉了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔装得真像，但现在又何必还要装呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "我知道他今天是真的醉了，绝不是装醉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "但你可知道他的酒量？他怎会醉得这么快？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔你这就不懂了，一个人喝酒时的心情若不好，体力又差，就算他酒量再好，也很容易被人灌醉的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你为何要灌醉他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔你也许不知道，这是爷爷的吩咐呀！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他现在行踪已露，要找他麻烦的人也不知有多少，这两天就要接二连三地来了，所以爷爷就想将他带到别的地方去避一避风头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "但二叔你也该知道他的脾气，若不灌醉他，怎么能把他带得走？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "老实说，你爷爷做的事，我实在有点不懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "不懂？什么地方不懂？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "李寻欢志气消沉，不愿见人的时候，他老人家总是想激他出手，现在李寻欢总算出手了，他老人家反而又要他去躲起来避风头。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔你这就错了，志气消沉和避风头完全是两回事，怎么可以一概而论？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "你可知道想要这颗头颅的人有多少么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "无论有多少人，除了上官金虹外，别的人又何足惧？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "二叔你又错了，敢在李寻欢脑袋上打主意的人，自然就绝不会是容易打的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "那些人都是些什么样的角色？你说给我听听。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "男的不说，先说女的，其中就有苗疆'大欢喜女菩萨'和关外'蓝蝎子'……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "百晓生重男轻女，兵器谱上不列女子高手，但这两个母夜叉的名字，二叔你总也该听过的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "蓝蝎子是青魔手的情人，大欢喜女菩萨是五毒童子的干娘，她们早已在打听李寻欢的行踪，若听说他在这里，一定会立刻赶来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "她们两人中只要有一个赶到，就够他受的了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "说完了女的，再说男的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "男的有上官金虹、吕凤先、荆无命，还有……还有个人二叔你一定猜不出是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "胡不归。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "胡不归？是不是那胡疯子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "不错，这人一向疯疯癫癫，用的是柄竹剑，据说他的剑法也跟他的人一样，疯疯癫癫的，有的精奇绝俗，妙到毫巅，有时却又糟得一塌糊涂，简直连看都看不得，所以百晓生作兵器谱时，才没有将他的名字列上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "高是真的，糟是假的……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "只不过此人一向不跟别人打交道，这次为何要找李寻欢的麻烦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "听说他是被龙啸云请出来的，龙啸云的师父以前好像帮过他的忙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "这人一向难找，谁也不知道他在哪里，龙啸云能找到他，本事倒真不小。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "就因为此人难找，所以龙啸云才会一去两年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你刚刚说的那吕凤先，就是兵器谱上名列第五的温侯银戟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "不错，他找的倒并不单只是李寻欢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "他还想找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "此人近年来练了几手很特别的功夫，所以凡是兵器谱上列名在他之前的人，他都想找来斗一斗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "那荆……荆……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "荆无命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "嗯，这荆无命，又是何许人也？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "荆无命就是上官金虹属下第一号的打手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "我怎么从未听说过他的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "此人出道才不过两年多，听爷爷说，武林后起一代的高手中，最厉害的两个人就是这荆无命和阿飞！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他用的也是剑，出手也和阿飞一样，又狠、又准、又快！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "除此之外，这人还有一样最可怕的地方！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他平时很少出手，但只要一和人交上手，就连自己的性命都不要了，每一招用的都是拼命的招式，他自称荆无命，意思就是说他这条命早已和人拼掉了，所以根本就不把自己的死活放在心上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你爷爷呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他老人家和我约好在城外见面……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "他老人家知道我一定有法子将李寻欢带去的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孙驼子",
      "listener": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "text": "你这小丫头倒真是个鬼灵精。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_xiao_hong",
      "speaker_name": "孙小红",
      "listener": "char_sun_tuo_zi",
      "text": "人家已经快二十了，二叔还说人家是小丫头。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 34,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    }
  ],
